  "aboutUs": {
    "title": "About Us",
    "description": "The Ramirez Restaurants are defining gastronomic venues in Siófok, where classical elegance meets modern hospitality. Our restaurants aim to provide a special experience for every guest – whether it's a lunch with friends, a family dinner, or even a business meeting. Alongside the flavors of international cuisine, our menu also features traditional Hungarian dishes, reimagined with a modern perspective. With our Gyros specialties, we also cater to lovers of Eastern flavors, while our hand-stretched, oven-baked pizzas evoke a classic Italian atmosphere. On our beverage menu, carefully selected quality wines, premium pálinkas, and special drinks await our guests. Our restaurant is an ideal choice for family, friends, birthday or business events, as well as for hosting larger parties and groups."
  },
